:<font size="15">בּדל</font></div>

===Pronunciation===
בּדל / bâdal / baw-dal'

===Etymology===
A primitive root; 

===Verb===
'''בּדל'''

# To [[divide]] (in various senses literally or figuratively, separate, distinguish, differ, select, etc.): - (make, put) difference, divide (asunder), (make) separate (self, -ation), sever (out), X utterly.

